Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store

Provides the classes and interfaces of the MEKON Instance-Store API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon for general description).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMatches
    Represents the results of an instance-matching query executed via an IStore object.
    IMatchesRank
    Represents a sub-set of the results of an instance-matching query executed via an IStore object, all of which have been assigned an identical ranking-value by the matching mechanism.
    IRegenInstance
    Represents a specific IFrame/ISlot network that has been regenerated from a serialized form, and hence may be partially or fully invalid with respect to the current model.
    IRegenPath
    Represents the path from the root-frame of a regenerated IFrame/ISlot network to a specific slot or slot-value within the network.
    IRegenType
    Represents the type of the root-frame of a specific IFrame/ISlot network that has been regenerated from a serialized form, and hence may be partially or fully invalid with respect to the current model.
    IStore
    Represents an instance-store associated with a MEKON Frames Model (FM).
    IStoreRegenReport
    Provides information concerning any IFrame/ISlot networks serialized on disk, that are now fully invalid or partially valid with respect to the current model.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IRegenStatus
    Represents the status of a specific IFrame/ISlot network that has been regenerated from a serialized form.

Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store Description

Provides the classes and interfaces of the MEKON Instance-Store API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon for general description).

NOTE: This is a companion package to the uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.motor package, with which it shares circular dependencies at the implementation level, though not at the API level. See uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon for further details.
